text: Rosi Sailer (born 20 August 1931) is an Austrian alpine skier. She competed in the women's slalom at the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Austria Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kitzbühel
